The paper addresses the problems of view synthesis and environment reconstruction, which are common topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The paper also mentions modeling inter-reflections and Fresnel effects, which are related to geometric modeling (cs.GT) and robotics (cs.RO). Finally, the paper discusses the use of low dynamic range imagery, which is a common topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
